-- AMR gets court OK to send restructuring plan to creditors for a vote
-- 
-- Tue Jun 4, 2013 12:23pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/06/04/us-amr-restructuring-idUSBRE9530VN20130604

 

 (Reuters) - American Airlines' bankrupt parent received court permission on Tuesday to send its restructuring plan to creditors for a vote. 
 Judge Sean Lane green-lighted AMR Corp's ( AAMRQ.PK ) plan, which involves merging with smaller carrier US Airways Group ( LCC.N ), at a hearing in U.S. Bankruptcy Court in Manhattan. (Reporting by Nick Brown and Bill Cheung; editing by John Wallace)